        {
            "title": "私債贖回潮是虛驚？星展資深經濟學家揭原因 且下半年川普有3大勝選盤算",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IvjDVUxdj5.AmlIFXENOAw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/42e627b4a0508b9c73e4d80d2f866db1\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A7%81%E5%82%B5%E8%B4%96%E5%9B%9E%E6%BD%AE%E6%98%AF%E8%99%9B%E9%A9%9A-%E6%98%9F%E5%B1%95%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%E6%8F%AD%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0-%E4%B8%94%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%9C%893%E5%A4%A7%E5%8B%9D%E9%81%B8%E7%9B%A4%E7%AE%97-113503839.html",
